  ],
  "body_blocks": [
    {
      "block_id": "b00002",
      "block_type": "article",
      "text": "第一条 为了规范深圳证券交易所(以下简称本所)股票期权(以下简称期权)合约条款管理,根据《深圳证券交易所股票期权试点交易规则》《深圳证券交易所 中国证券登记结算有限责任公司股票期权试点风险控制管理办法》及其他有关规定,制定本指引。",
      "style": "",
      "source_kind": "paragraph",
      "source_page_start": 1,
      "source_page_end": 1,
      "start_char": 0,
      "end_char": 115,
      "region": "body"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b00003",
      "block_type": "article",
      "text": "第二条 本指引所称合约条款,主要包括合约简称、合约编码、合约代码、合约标的、合约类型、到期月份、合约单位、行权价格、行权方式、交割方式等。",
      "style": "",
      "source_kind": "paragraph",
      "source_page_start": 1,
      "source_page_end": 1,
      "start_char": 117,
      "end_char": 186,
      "region": "body"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b00004",
      "block_type": "article",
      "text": "第三条 在本所上市交易的股票、交易型开放式基金以及经中国证券监督管理委员会(以下简称中国证监会)批准的其他证券品种,可以作为期权合约的标的物(以下简称合约标的)。",
      "style": "",
      "source_kind": "paragraph",
      "source_page_start": 1,
      "source_page_end": 1,
      "start_char": 188,
      "end_char": 269,
      "region": "body"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b00005",
      "block_type": "article",
      "text": "第四条 合约代码包含合约标的、合约类型、到期月份、行权价格等要素。期权合约的合约代码共有 20 位,具体组成为:第 1至第 6 位为标的证券代码;第 7 位为 C(Call)或者 P(Put),分别表示认购期权或者认沽期权;第 8、9 位表示到期年份的后两位数字,第 10、11 位表示到期月份(分别用 01 至 12 代替);第 12 位为“ M” ,代表月合约序列;第 13 至 18 位表示期权行权价格,保留三位小数。第 19 位为合约版本号,首次调整改为“ A” ,再次调整改为“ B” ,依此类推。预留第 20 位。",
      "style": "",
      "source_kind": "paragraph",
      "source_page_start": 1,
      "source_page_end": 1,
      "start_char": 271,
      "end_char": 534,
      "region": "body"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b00007",
      "block_type": "article",
      "text": "第五条 合约简称与合约代码相对应,由合约标的简称、合约类型、到期月份、行权价格等要素组成。",
      "style": "",
      "source_kind": "paragraph",
      "source_page_start": 2,
      "source_page_end": 2,
      "start_char": 536,
      "end_char": 581,
      "region": "body"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b00008",
      "block_type": "article",
      "text": "第六条 合约编码用于唯一识别和记录期权合约。期权合约编码由 8 位数字构成,合约标的为交易型开放式基金的,从 90000001至 91999999 按顺序对挂牌合约进行编码;合约标的为股票的,从92000001 至 99999999 按顺序对挂牌合约进行编码。",
      "style": "",
      "source_kind": "paragraph",
      "source_page_start": 2,
      "source_page_end": 2,
      "start_char": 583,
      "end_char": 713,
      "region": "body"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b00009",
      "block_type": "article",
      "text": "第七条 合约类型包括认购期权和认沽期权。",
      "style": "",
      "source_kind": "paragraph",
      "source_page_start": 2,
      "source_page_end": 2,
      "start_char": 715,
      "end_char": 735,
      "region": "body"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b00010",
      "block_type": "article",
      "text": "第八条 合约到期月份为当月、下月及随后两个季月,共 4 个月份同时挂牌交易。",
      "style": "",
      "source_kind": "paragraph",
      "source_page_start": 2,
      "source_page_end": 2,
      "start_char": 737,
      "end_char": 775,
      "region": "body"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b00011",
      "block_type": "article",
      "text": "第九条 合约标的为交易型开放式基金的,每张期权合约对应10000 份基金份额。合约标的为股票的,每张期权合约对应 1000股股票。",
      "style": "",
      "source_kind": "paragraph",
      "source_page_start": 2,
      "source_page_end": 2,
      "start_char": 777,
      "end_char": 842,
      "region": "body"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b00012",
      "block_type": "article",
      "text": "第十条 本所以期权合约标的前一交易日收盘价为基准,确立平值期权行权价格,再依照行权价格间距依序加挂新行权价格合约,使得行权价格高于(低于)平值行权价格的期权合约至少达到4 个。",
      "style": "",
      "source_kind": "paragraph",
      "source_page_start": 2,
      "source_page_end": 2,
      "start_char": 844,
      "end_char": 932,
      "region": "body"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b00013",
      "block_type": "article",
      "text": "第十一条 行权价格间距根据期权合约标的收盘价格分区间设置,其收盘价与行权价格间距的对应关系为:",
      "style": "",
      "source_kind": "paragraph",
      "source_page_start": 2,
      "source_page_end": 2,
      "start_char": 934,
      "end_char": 981,
      "region": "body"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b00014",
      "block_type": "paragraph",
      "text": "(一)合约标的为交易型开放式基金的,3 元或以下为 0.05 元,3 元至 5 元(含)为 0.1 元,5 元至 10 元(含)为 0.25 元,10 元至 20 元(含)为 0.5 元,20 元至 50 元(含)为 1 元,50 元至 100元(含)为 2.5 元,超过 100 元的为 5 元;",
      "style": "",
      "source_kind": "paragraph",
      "source_page_start": 2,
      "source_page_end": 2,
      "start_char": 983,
      "end_char": 1132,
      "region": "body"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b00016",
      "block_type": "paragraph",
      "text": "(二)合约标的为股票的,2 元或以下为 0.1 元,2 元至 5 元(含)为 0.25 元,5 元至 10 元(含)为 0.5 元,10 元至 20 元(含)为 1 元,20 元至 50 元(含)为 2.5 元,50 元至 100 元(含)为 5元,超过 100 元的为 10 元。",
      "style": "",
      "source_kind": "paragraph",
      "source_page_start": 3,
      "source_page_end": 3,
      "start_char": 1134,
      "end_char": 1275,
      "region": "body"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b00017",
      "block_type": "article",
      "text": "第十二条 期权合约采用到期日行权方式。",
      "style": "",
      "source_kind": "paragraph",
      "source_page_start": 3,
      "source_page_end": 3,
      "start_char": 1277,
      "end_char": 1296,
      "region": "body"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b00018",
      "block_type": "article",
      "text": "第十三条 期权合约采用实物交割方式。本所另有规定的除外。",
      "style": "",
      "source_kind": "paragraph",
      "source_page_start": 3,
      "source_page_end": 3,
      "start_char": 1298,
      "end_char": 1326,
      "region": "body"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b00019",
      "block_type": "article",
      "text": "第十四条 期权合约到期日为到期月份的第四个星期三,遇法定节假日、本所休市日的,顺延至次一交易日。",
      "style": "",
      "source_kind": "paragraph",
      "source_page_start": 3,
      "source_page_end": 3,
      "start_char": 1328,
      "end_char": 1376,
      "region": "body"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b00020",
      "block_type": "article",
      "text": "第十五条 本指引由本所负责解释。",
      "style": "",
      "source_kind": "paragraph",
      "source_page_start": 3,
      "source_page_end": 3,
      "start_char": 1378,
      "end_char": 1394,
      "region": "body"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b00021",
      "block_type": "article",
      "text": "第十六条 本指引自发布之日起施行。",
      "style": "",
      "source_kind": "paragraph",
      "source_page_start": 3,
      "source_page_end": 3,
      "start_char": 1396,
      "end_char": 1413,
      "region": "body"
    }
  ],
  "appendices": [],
